                  </persName>
            . I am a shoemaker, in the employ of Fimister. Chambers met me as I was going to the shop- I followed the prisoner; he ran towards Brook-street, and I pursued him, crying Stop thief! in a short time I saw him take a boot from under his coat, and throw it among some rubbish - the officer pursued, and took him in the Commercial-road; I took up this boot, and followed him - he was taken in two minutes afterwards; this is my master's.</p>
